reviews.reviewText: Ok we celebrate Christmas a few days early cause of scheduling. My nephews (twins) LOVE them. Gotten a police and a fire one. At this moment they only know about the plane; they don’t know about any of the accessories that came with it. So here’s a tip if you have a child who is 2 buy this; it’s only 3 and up cause of the small parts and you can introduce those part to them later on when they’re older. Like all the accessories that came with this is unopened and probably be months before they get opened.Also I don’t have any pics or videos I try not to be on my phone when visiting.
